                            <ul class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 space-y-2 text-sm">
                                <li>• Senior engineers only</li>
                                <li>• Talk directly to who's building it</li>
                                <li>• No management overhead</li>
                                <li>• No account managers</li>
                                <li>• No corporate nonsense</li>
                            </ul>
