                <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-4">Recent Projects</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
                        Projects we've shipped across medical devices, industrial systems, and precision instruments.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-8">
                        <!-- Medical Device Project -->
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-orange-500/20 hover:border-orange-500 dark:hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all duration-400 group">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-500 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full shadow-md group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-all duration-300">Medical Device</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Ultrasound Imaging System Motor Control</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                Client's previous engineering firm delivered a 5-axis positioning system that failed EMC testing and couldn't hit 0.1mm positioning accuracy. We redesigned it from scratch with proper motor drive topology, EMI filtering, and 6-layer PCB stackup.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-2">Results:</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Sub-0.1mm positioning accuracy achieved</li>
                                    <li>• IEC 60601-1-2 EMC pre-compliance passed</li>
                                    <li>• $10K+ annual cost savings from design optimization</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <button class="mt-4 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-700 dark:hover:text-orange-300 font-medium text-sm flex items-center expand-btn" >
