                                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">System Architecture:</p>
                                        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
                                            <li>• 5-axis precision motion control</li>
                                            <li>• 6-layer PCB stackup for EMI control</li>
                                            <li>• Dedicated power supply filtering</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">Key Problems Solved:</p>
                                        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
                                            <li>• Motor ripple interference elimination</li>
                                            <li>• Power supply noise reduction</li>
                                            <li>• Medical device EMC compliance</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">Similar precision control systems used in robotics, semiconductor manufacturing, and medical imaging equipment.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Industrial IoT Project -->
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-orange-500/20 hover:border-orange-500 dark:hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all duration-400 group">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-400 text-white dark:text-slate-900 text-sm font-bold rounded-full shadow-md group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:bg-orange-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">Industrial IoT</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Industrial Power Monitoring System</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                Client's legacy power distribution equipment lacked monitoring capabilities. We retrofitted their units with custom hardware for real-time current sensing, embedded Linux controller, and web-based dashboard. Transformed basic equipment into smart monitoring systems.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-2">Results:</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Real-time power monitoring and predictive alerts</li>
                                    <li>• Significant revenue increase from enhanced product value</li>
                                    <li>• Competitive positioning in smart infrastructure market</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <button class="mt-4 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-700 dark:hover:text-orange-300 font-medium text-sm flex items-center expand-btn" >
