                                            <li>• TCP/IP web interface</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">Performance:</p>
                                        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
                                            <li>• 0.1% current measurement accuracy</li>
                                            <li>• Predictive maintenance algorithms</li>
                                            <li>• Automatic alarm conditions</li>
                                            <li>• Less than 1 year ROI from completion</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <!-- Scientific Instrument Project -->
                        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border-2 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-lg hover:scale-[1.03] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-orange-500/20 hover:border-orange-500 dark:hover:border-orange-400 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-slate-700 transition-all duration-400 group">
                            <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-600 dark:bg-slate-500 text-white text-sm font-bold rounded-full shadow-md group-hover:shadow-lg group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:bg-orange-500 transition-all duration-300">Scientific Instrument</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Gravitometer Controller Replacement</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                30-year-old gravitometer controller died. Original company was out of business, no documentation, and a new system would cost $200K+. Had to save $150K worth of analog sensors.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-2">Results:</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Better precision than the original</li>
                                    <li>• Saved $150K+ in equipment costs</li>
                                    <li>• 15+ years additional operational life</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <button class="mt-4 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 hover:text-orange-700 dark:hover:text-orange-300 font-medium text-sm flex items-center expand-btn">
