                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Audio-Reactive LED System</h3>
                            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                                Startup wanted to build LED lights that react to music in real-time. Needed sub-5ms response, 4+ hour battery, mobile app control, and FCC compliance.
                            </p>
                            <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-900 p-3 rounded-lg border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-2">Results:</p>
                                <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 space-y-1">
                                    <li>• Sub-5ms audio response achieved</li>
                                    <li>• 4+ hour battery life delivered</li>
                                    <li>• FCC compliance testing ready</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
