                                            <li>• Sub-5ms response optimization</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <p class="font-medium text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">System Specs:</p>
                                        <ul class="space-y-1 ml-2">
                                            <li>• 160 strips x 4 channels = 640 zones</li>
                                            <li>• 100ft Bluetooth range</li>
                                            <li>• Mobile app control interface</li>
                                            <li>• FCC EMI compliance design</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-500">Main challenge: DSP processing complexity for real-time control of 640+ LED zones while maintaining sub-5ms audio latency.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
